\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112414\charrsid14039999 Mary\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  church, they were very good to us there. And there was always jumble sales or something. And mother made a point of going 
