 shops were, she used to say, only wish I'd got fourpence to spare. I said, what for? She said, you want some new }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112414\charrsid14039999 vests}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
. You could get calico - for two three a yard she called it. I said, what does two three mean mum? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112414\charrsid14039999 Just twopence three farthings a yard.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
