\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 I was quite young. I'd started school but I just can't rememb
er exactly how old I was. Oh yes, it must be ten because she'd have been in Union Road, I went there when we were ten. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Do you know how much your mother paid a week for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 It wasn't a lot, perhaps five shillings, perhaps less than that some
times, and she'd perhaps finish one off before she'd have another but - if that lady saw our shoes were getting shabby she said, you'll have to have a new pair. Or if me brother went she'd look - see about you John, she said. She was such a sweet woman.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 She took it terribly seriously didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
Yes, she - of course - all the people she dealt with were - were all in the same - boat you see. But she couldn't bear to see - the - I've never had a pair of shoes to fit, none of us had. They'd had had to buy them at Smeddon market, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5112414\charrsid14039999 seconds}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
. Somebody else - and when the treads in - your foot's not right is it. You see, and she knew all about this, this lady did. I used to run messages for her sometimes too when I couldn't pay the bill, she said, can you 
