\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did your father help with anything to do with your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Could he mend shoes or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 No. I tell you the only thing father ever mended was the clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 But your mother was very good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Oh yes. Yes, yes. Could she do things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 He always got up first, made the 
fire and took her a cup of tea. He used to think it was wonderful. But it wasn't really wonderful considering all she did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 So that was all he did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 As long as I can ever remember father always made the fire - in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did he do anything about decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
Oh no. No. He didn't do any - just the clock and making the fire and taking her a cup of tea. And as for - me brother grew older and - one of the girls got married young, and she and my brother and her husband would a say, oh it 
does want wallpapering mum, can you afford a bit of cheap wallpaper, we'll come down and do it for you one weekend. And they always did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Before then your mother would have done it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 My mother did - she couldn't do wallpapering. Because she had - she hadn't the time It wasn't done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did your father help with the children at all, did he bath you or undress you or dress you or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 That was thought to be woman's work was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 That was, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did he tell you stories?
\par 
