No, not - he used to tell us about the men he worked with, which I thought was so funny. And mother used to rib at me for laughing. They all had funny names. This man came to the door one day and mother said, see who that is. And thi
s man said - is Enoch in? Well I'd never heard me father's Christian name. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 You didn't know it was Enoch?
