 with a message once and this aunt said, tell your mother it's about time she came to see me. I said, mother auntie says, she'd like to see you. Oh, she says, one day I'll go - I'll go. But I had to keep on about it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4399113\charrsid14039999 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  know, and then one day I said, come o
n mum, go and take me to see auntie. And she did go. But open for all. I never went again with her. I went myself. I used to go there quite a lot. But - I don't think she wanted anything else. 'Cos I said to her, it's a lonely life, what pleasure do you h
