. And for their suppers, dad and mum, they had suppers we never had any, we just had the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4399113\charrsid14039999 cocoa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
, but mother and father, they had a slice of dried bread, no buyer on it, and a tiny little bit of cheese. And that was a real luxury to them.
