{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4399113\charrsid14039999 more}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  you see, didn't take any notice, so I had sufficient. We weren't she -
