ave us all jumping op and down together. If you finished first - I want to get down - I want to go out and play - and another one he was a bit slower than I was, or the other sister the other side - and when the plates were finished we put our knives and 
forks by the side of the plate then we'd look at mother, may we get down mother please? Have you finished? Yes. Yes, you can get down.
