dn't sort of - she'd got no patience. With - well of course after all that I wonder that she'd got any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6840067\charrsid14039999 left}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
 at all. She was really - a marvel.
