nything you don't want her to tell the family you couldn't do because - the first time you did anything that she didn't like - out it would all come. And you did say, oh mum you wouldn't tell them. But I went I must tell you that funny little bit. I'd had
 bronchitis, oh I went and I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6840067\charrsid14039999 was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
