, and had to sort of look to see what his face looked like. But sometimes - he'd be very funny. 'Specially when he talked about these funny old men he worked with. And - he made us die with laughing. But you - you were 1 you weren't allowed to act in - th
at'll be quite enough, you see, sort of.
