Oh yes, if there was a - anything a bit better that you had that was your Sunday clothes and that was sacred and you could not put it on for anything else in the week. You had to keep it. It had to be taken off and brus
hed and put away and just put on on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did you play games on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
No, not ever. We weren't allowed. We weren't allowed even to read books. Mother just let us look at these two religious books she - I think it was Home }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14505167\charrsid14039999 Companion}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  or Famil
y Circle - something of these - like Woman such as - only not so big. Not so flamboyant either. It was all in plain print. And - she liked them and we had to ask if she - if we may look at them. But you couldn't - bet - we - when we was knitting }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14505167\charrsid14039999 crazy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  or a
nything like that, and once brought some knitting out and she said, have you forgotten what day it is? And I said, no mother, it's }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15204605\charrsid14039999 Sunday.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  You see, I hadn't registered her so me mind was just concentrated on doing it. So she said, well you'll put that way until then. What you don't get done in the week you won't do on Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Was the work the same?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Well we just did the washing up. But we weren't allowed to do any housework. No. We }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15204605\charrsid14039999 worked}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999  - it was well done at the weekend and it had got to last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 So your parents did think it was wrong to do these things on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Oh very wrong, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 No, they never went. But they were quite sure it was right for us to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 What denomination?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 They never went at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 I don't remember them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Were there any Sunday school outings?
