\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Yes, we were in - this little choir - always at this church mission. Our Vicar at St Marks, he was getting on a
nd some of the boys were a bit - unruly and he would not have us in the church, he said it distracted the other people. So the Captain said - he said, well I think I can manage them. He was young. And you know we - we loved that man. He - he didn't sort o
f make it think it - make us think we were being made to do these things. Now come on dear, shall we do }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15204605\charrsid14039999 so}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
 and so? And you did it. We had flower services we had concerts - oh - I loved that little mission I -
