he pictures two evenings we went to the - we really enjoyed it. And - then I'd got to put fifty hours in at the City Hospital. Oh you had to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2979937\charrsid14039999 do}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
