cture, you see, and - I did the full fifty. And then of course I had to go and tell the doctor. Just put paid to my career. He said, you've got a chest like this, he said, I couldn't possibly. He said, and I wasn't - in any case he said, you won't be stro
ng enough to be on your feet all day. Because I'd been in a sitting job down all the time and me chest was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2979937\charrsid14039999 dreadfully}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
 bad then and I really worried about that. But I didn't mind of course Oh well, we all have the things. And then the next - who was it, some
one came and said, well go in a first aid post. You will be doing something. And I went - you know the entrance to the City Hospital, it used to be part of the old work house. Now what did they call it? There's a name for it. I can't just - on - as you go
