. You see, we should - we only had two lots of casualties, but it's a lot of money to pay out. It was moving more towards the centre
, to Birmingham and - all round there so they said well - they couldn't keep us on, there was six of us and a - a sister in charge. So - they said, well we're going to do something about women in the Fire Service, you'd better go there. And I was one - I 
