, don't be such - a fuss, I said, it give me the willies. I said, we have to live as we can. I said, well you've got a full job on I can }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987527\charrsid14039999 assure}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
