\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 You told me earlier on how you spent your time as a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987527\charrsid14039999 schoolgirl}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 , your spare time, was it any different when you'd left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 We
ll of course I didn't - so much time, I'd got some own time for a little bit after we'd had our tea and washed up whatever we'd got to do. Or if we'd got some chebonning I'd perhaps do a bit of chebonning and - Alice watched over me because I wasn't well,
 and she'd say, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987527\charrsid14039999 you\rquote ll}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
 sit there 'til you're so pale. Get out in the fresh air a bit. And then I'd perhaps go out on the street and play with the others for half an hour or so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 When you'd started work were you still the same sort of person about playing out or did you go out with a bump?
