Oh - no, we didn't go out. I was - I was very much interested in playing round. Used to play round a lamp - we got an old bat and we used to go up there and play - about four or five of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did you go out in the evening when you were working at first?
