\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8407077 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Did your parents meet your}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15994928\charrsid14039999  friends,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
