\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 She was the only one. I - you'll have to ask mo
ther first, see, I'd say, Could I bring Florrie mum? And she'd say, oh my goodness, that's another one. You know, but she didn't say it nastily. And I would say again, well can I. She'd say, yes, all right then. Mind you we had nothing any different, brea
d and - butter and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12987527\charrsid14039999 Hartley\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
 blackcurrant jam. But she was such a nice girl. They were just a working family like we were and she'd got a lot of brothers and sisters.
