No, not really, no, she didn't do that. But - there was - father'd say, well remember what time you get in and what time we expect you in. I - we 
would say, all right dad, all right mum. And we'd be off. But - were we to be a little later. Where have you been to this time of night? We've been walking, we've been talking. Oh - I've seen her look as me dad as much as to say, you'll not get anything o
ut of him, they won't say.
