And - so he had a look at it and he tugged it, he said, oh that's all right. And of course George had so many recruits and he'd filed them all in and the - to show them how to punch it correctly, I didn't even know there was such a thing as a corre
ct way, did you, and of course being a man when he'd finished them all and they'd all filed out the hut, it was just - September - it was October - it was just a month to the day that we'd been married, and - as he walked by it going out he gave it a wond
