\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15820647 AW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 No. No. Not then. No, I'd been married just over two years when I - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15994928\charrsid14039999 
