 you got nowhere? She said, can't they put you up at the hospital? I said, no, they said the nurses are sleeping two in a bed. She said, well we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6301576\charrsid14039999 ain\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
