 Oh don't insult us. We're only charmed to have you. And - he was the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6301576\charrsid14039999 superintendent}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 
