 Post, the Nottingham Evening Post, and he was - they gave them so much money if they went round to each house and got an order for one. But you'd got to get it for a whole week and they gave them - not a proper wage but a sort of - bonus on all that they
 could get. And the things George used to say, and me brother was - he was out of work at the same time, used to go together. Used to say - I'll - I'll bath the baby for you missus if you'll sign this form.
