Come here, I'll peel the potatoes for you,luv. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16006220\charrsid14039999 Well - those boys - I knew about - 
there was George and my brother John and about two more of them, they had the time of their lives. They really enjoyed it. And they got a few shillings and they were satisfied. And then when that - that dried up of course. Couldn't expect it to last. And 
