\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6301576\charrsid14039999 And - and then he got a job - he had - he was out of work a long, long while before they got - he got - always got this pension for the loss of the eye and with 
what I could earn you see, and he'd got - he'd get so much - on the dole, you see, the three together, when Joyce started to work of course, she went in to Bairnswear and it wasn't much but one with the other and I'd always been used to being careful so t
