he sun never penetrated to those houses and - Joyce had pneumonia and Grace had got bronchitis and I was ill and this doctor who came, I - he said - you know, these houses aren't fit to bring children up in, he said, I don't know what - whatever do you st
ay here for? I said, well you just tell me where I can get another one will you and I'll go. So he says, well, he said, something should be done, you want to get out. Sherwood or Ma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1334943\charrsid14039999 pperl}{
